summary: In lieu of all of the very deserved paise for the ever delightful Mr Sheen, I feel a great need to remind/inform everyone of his...
body:
In lieu of all of the very deserved paise for the ever delightful Mr Sheen, I feel a great need to remind/inform everyone of his status as a self-proclaimed super fan of the hilariously awful Belinda Blinked series of….erotica?

To the uninitiated, they are a series of absolutely horrendous, marvelous books (of a sort), read aloud by the author’s son and his friends on the podcast My Dad Wrote A Porno, and it is simultaniously the best and worst thing to ever happen to humanity. As I said, Michael Sheen is a huge fan and was a guest on a glorious episode, where he made an impassioned plea to consider the Belinda Blinked series on par with Shakespeare. Or, in other words, he went

It is great, and you should give it a listen, QED.
